.DT
news
Discworld player help
news

.SH Name
.SI 5
news - The announcements system for Discworld.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
news [none|list|review|<num>|help]
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
News is the command to find out what things have changed recently on Discworld.  When something changes that will affect players an announcement will be posted.
.EP

.SH Parameters
.SP 5 5
News can take a number of parameters.
.EP
.S0 10 10 -20
	none	With no parameter, news will display the next unread news item.
	list	Will list all unread news items (may be shortened to "l")
	review	Will list all news items (may be shortened to "r")
	<num>	Will read the news item number <num>
	help	Will give a brief list of the syntax (my be shortened to "h" or "?")
.EO

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
none.
.EP
